36
00:02:51,278 --> 00:03:02,584
We were fortunate enough to, with a good paying union job, my father was able to get, became a member of the machinist union and we were solidly middle class.

37
00:03:02,644 --> 00:03:04,365
So it was always important to help those

38
00:03:05,061 --> 00:03:06,602
around us that weren't doing as well.

39
00:03:08,162 --> 00:03:13,825
