40
00:03:14,125 --> 00:03:17,646
And obviously, as an adult, you have to start figuring out how to take care of yourself.

41
00:03:17,767 --> 00:03:19,047
So I did that for a few years.

42
00:03:19,487 --> 00:03:22,909
But I was always interested in advocating for different things.

43
00:03:23,969 --> 00:03:28,551
Reproductive rights was something that was really under attack in the 90s with

44
00:03:30,903 --> 00:03:34,786
taxon clinics and things like that, so I was an escort for a while.

45
00:03:36,527 --> 00:03:43,893
I had a lot of gay friends, and when marriage equality came up, it was something that was really important to me as well, so I advocated for that.

46
00:03:44,833 --> 00:03:48,256
