47
00:03:48,336 --> 00:03:53,159
I was working in healthcare as an administrator, and I was doing help there.

48
00:03:53,179 --> 00:03:55,621
I was helping people get tests approved.

49
00:03:55,641 --> 00:03:57,963
I was helping people understand and navigate

50
00:03:58,512 --> 00:04:13,500
