00:12:10,538 --> 00:12:21,746
I kind of wonder how you think about just those themes of equity inclusion and how that, you know, that position in the state house could help, you know, with more progress in those areas.

119
00:12:22,166 --> 00:12:23,907
Yeah, I mean, let's be honest.

